<bibRefCitation id="492C4B54C07C4B1EFBD54D83FB2F34F9" author="ICZN &amp; International Code of Zoological Nomenclature" box="[1044,1176,214,238]" pageId="29" pageNumber="28" refId="ref44854" refString="(ICZN) International Code of Zoological Nomenclature. 1999. 4 th Edition. Adopted by the International Union of Biological Sciences. The International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature; London, United Kingdom. 306 p." type="book" year="1999">ICZN (1999)</bibRefCitation>
